channel.title: People Cannont run my download client
channel.description:
Alright so i've made my server download client. I am using Projeck Ecko. When i sent it to a few friends so they could connect to the server, they click run and it comes with an error saying "Error, Could not find or load main class client, Press any key to continue" I'd really appreciate it if someone could help me out here. My skype is Jordan.TateRS if you wanna talk on skype or you could just post help on here. Either way i appreciate it.
Thanks, Jordan

item.title: People Cannont run my download client
item.dc:creator: @Doggie_Skill Doggie Skill
item.description:
@Doggie_Skill wrote:

They probably need to change the JDK or jre version. Right click run, click edit, and change the Jdk or jre.
